<li>Hubert is the name of Harlan Pepper&#39;s (<a href="" title="Christopher Guest">Christopher Guest</a>) bloodhound in the cult comedy <a href="" title="Best in Show (film)"><i>Best in Show</i> (2000 film)</a></li>
<li>In the animated show <a href="" title="King of the Hill">King of the Hill</a>, Hank Hill&#39;s beloved dog Ladybird is a bloodhound</li>
<li>The abilities of bloodhounds were put to the test in two episodes of <a href="" title="Mythbusters">Mythbusters</a>.</li>
<li>The bloodhound face is used as a logo for the main antagonist &#34;Elite Hunting Club&#34; in <a href="" title="Hostel (2005 film)">Hostel (2005 film)</a>, <a href="" title="Hostel: Part II">Hostel: Part II</a>, and <a href="" title="Hostel: Part III">Hostel: Part III</a> respectively.</li>
