&#60;!-- The category inventions is used for discovery , innovation etc As an encompassing term to avoid creating too many categories (go check American inventions for reference) . Monks at the St-Hubertus monastary spent generations breeding this dog , it didn&#39;t suddenly pop up in a field. The process of selectively breeding until the desired result is achieved is as close to &#34;invention&#34; as it gets with animals or plants. The person that makes it his life&#39;s work to cross pollinate maize to come up with a strain that&#39;s mold resistant , that strain will be his achievement . Just as this dog is the mainly achievement by the St Hubertus abbey monks. --&#62;</p>
